sub_fields.instructions: Featured callout that appears at the bottom of the Submenu

sub_fields.label: Is Descriptive Submenu
sub_fields.name: is_descriptive_submenu
sub_fields.instructions: Should only ever be selected on second-level menus. Will be ignored otherwise.

sub_fields.label: Menu Item Tag
sub_fields.name: menu_item_tag
sub_fields.instructions: Optional featured tag next to the menu item label.

fields.label: Conversion Reference
fields.name: conversion_reference
fields.instructions: Optional. Add a featured asset (image, video, animation) or form to the conversion panel.

fields.label: Image Max Height
fields.name: image_max_height
fields.instructions: Number, in pixels. Image will stretch to full-width, so if the height is limited, it may crop vertically

sub_fields.label: Media Layout
sub_fields.name: media_layout
sub_fields.instructions: Allows the Featured Media to overflow the bottom of the hero container

sub_fields.label: Value Prefix
sub_fields.name: value_prefix
sub_fields.instructions: Optional special characters added to the start of the value: $, +, etc.

sub_fields.label: Value Suffix
sub_fields.name: value_suffix
sub_fields.instructions: Optional special characters added to the end of the value: %, +, etc.

sub_fields.label: Card Image
sub_fields.name: card_image
sub_fields.instructions:
Should have a transparent background, ideal 2:1 aspect ratio.
Will stretch to the edges of the card.

fields.label: Card Count
fields.name: card_count
fields.instructions: How many cards should be automatically displayed?

fields.label: Auto Scroll
fields.name: auto_scroll
fields.instructions: Optional. Automatically scroll through the slides every 8s

fields.label: Auto Scroll
fields.name: auto_scroll
fields.instructions: Optional. Automatically Scroll to next tab after 8s

fields.label: Logo (Dark Mode)
fields.name: logo_dark
fields.instructions: Optional. Logo to be used on dark backgrounds

sub_fields.label: Show Legal Disclaimer
sub_fields.name: show_legal_disclaimer
sub_fields.instructions: Shows a disclaimer below author bio on a blog post

fields.label: Title
fields.name: title
fields.instructions: Optional. Can override the Post Type title in a testimonial card.

fields.label: Featured Image
fields.name: featured_image
fields.instructions: Optional. Aspect Ratio for Testimonial Cards: 2x3

fields.label: Rating
fields.name: rating
fields.instructions: Optional. Used in nested testimonial cards

fields.label: Tag
fields.name: tag
fields.instructions: Optional. Is displayed next to the menu item in blue.

fields.label: Section ID
fields.name: section_id
fields.instructions:
Optional section ID.
Used in anchoring to sections/components. Should be unique to the page its on. Should be "slugified" - lowercase and hyphenated, no other special characters

fields.label: Background Images
fields.name: background_images
fields.instructions:
Optional. If there is one image, it will be placed at the selected position and fill the whole section (without stretching).
If there are multiple images, they will be placed at their respective location and take 1/n of the container, where n is the total number of images.

sub_fields.label: Position
sub_fields.name: position
sub_fields.instructions: Images will be full section height. The width will not be allowed to stretch beyond the original aspect ratio.

fields.label: Section Padding
fields.name: section_padding
fields.instructions: Components come with default padding, this gives the ability to override those settings. Only create one override per device

sub_fields.label: Disabled (By Default)
sub_fields.name: disabled
sub_fields.instructions: Should be used only in components where there is logic in the component that will enable the button

fields.label: Title
fields.name: title
fields.instructions: bold - highlights the text with a gradient color dependent on the section theme

sub_fields.label: Media Position
sub_fields.name: media_position
sub_fields.instructions: When screens get smaller, how should the image cropping behave? What part of the image should remain centered?

fields.label: Showcase Cards
fields.name: showcase_cards
fields.instructions: Optional. Will add full-width cards to the listing component.
